* Connections and\nForeign Catalogs
** Connection
***_ Stores technical details to reach external DB
***_ JDBC URL, host, port, credentials
***_ Created once, reused for multiple catalogs
***_ Supported: PostgreSQL, MySQL, Snowflake, BigQuery
** Foreign catalog
***_ Mirrors external database in Unity Catalog
***_ References a connection
***_ Specifies which external database to mirror
***_ Uses catalog.schema.table naming
** Key separation
***_ Connection = how to connect
***_ Foreign catalog = what to expose
@endmindmap
